00:00:01.939 --> 00:00:03.210
"My name is Paul Sandberg.

00:00:03.210 --> 00:00:06.000
I'm an actor, teacher and singer in the New
York City area.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.589
For more information, please visit my website
